{"tid":1811438,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解黃色經濟圈無包括歌手","createTime":"2020-01-04T16:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T01:07:45.000Z","uid":263648,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee1097d57378e16f452a5e8b1eb863c3575cf0e","tid":1811438,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:40:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">點解唔可以，自己歌手自己撐。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n馬蹄露可以做王妃、黃色歌手一樣可以做天王、天后。<br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以發起，一人出$8買一首歌，香港人養得起有骨氣嘅歌手有餘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">尤其係仲唱緊香港語的本地歌手。</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>以下歌手好值得支持 (歌曲只係建議，自行決定、排名無先後)：-</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n莊正 - 開放世界 (因理大救人被告暴動; 剛攞咗叱吒新人獎) - 首選買佢的歌<br />\n<br />\n方皓玟 - 人話、假使世界原來不像你預期、願<br />\n<br />\nRubberband - 漫長、天光了 (天光了有一個改咗歌詞的版本)<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩 - 是有種人<br />\n<br />\n達明 - 回憶有罪<br />\n<br />\n滅火器 - 傷城記（因為林夕填詞）<br />\n<br />\nLMF - 二零一九<br />\n<br />\n周國賢 - 凡夫的樂章、今生不回家、Children Song<br />\n<br />\n阮民安 - 煲底之約 (在iTunes唔覺有佢; 有其他方法就支持下)<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲有話我知，我再置頂。<br />\n<br />\n有餘錢應先捐星火、立場、守孩、支援手足等。"},{"pid":"0e2fb7397059338cc34775e33652f760c4d41250","tid":1811438,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n玩緊未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"222582a52bd0d91b2ab5142ecf42e3248ebe071c","tid":1811438,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T16:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30a2893a4211dc7fa50a5537d981392bc2b9fc33","tid":1811438,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2fb7397059338cc34775e33652f760c4d41250","tid":1811438,"ui